metadata.name: Ultimate Enma Chan
metadata.description:
The theme this time was "memorial services". At first, I had no intention to do so, but then I realized that this is what I wanted to do.

In my old job, I had to deal with the death of people.
I have heard from many bereaved families.
Most of them were sad and regretful, but sometimes I heard their voices of joy.
Each person has many thoughts and stories to tell.

These experiences have greatly influenced my view of life and death, my personality, and my artwork.
